OL,3,CInquest into death of dog walker, 80,
OL,4,Cinvolved in park attack opens
OL,6,FAn inquest into the death of an 80-
OL,7,Fyear-old grandfather who was assaulted
OL,8,Fin a park metres away from his home in
OL,9,FLeicester has been opened and then
OL,10,Fadjourned for criminal proceedings to
OL,11,Ftake place.
OL,13,FA 14-year-old boy has been charged
OL,14,Fwith the murder of Bhim Kohli, a
OL,15,Fgrandfather who was attacked while out
OL,16,Fwalking his dog in Franklin Park in
OL,17,FLeicester in September.
