OL,3,CInquest into death of dog walker, 80,
OL,4,Cinvolved in park attack opens
OL,6,FCoroner Ivan Cartwright opened the
OL,7,Finquest into his death at Leicester
OL,8,FCoroner's Court on Thursday and told
OL,9,Ffamily members who attended the short
OL,10,Fhearing that it was now adjourned.
OL,12,FMr Cartwright said: "Today I'm opening
OL,13,Fthe inquest and suspending the inquest
OL,14,Finto the death of Mr Bhim Kohli.
OL,16,F"I'm aware that a 14-year-old male was
OL,17,Fcharged with the offence of murder and
OL,18,Fthere is a criminal trial listed to
OL,19,Ftake place in February 2025.
