OL,6,F"So at this stage I'm statutorily
OL,7,Fobliged to suspend the inquest."
OL,9,FA preliminary cause of death had
OL,10,Fpreviously been given as a neck
OL,11,Finjury, pending further tests, but Mr
OL,12,FCartwright told the court that a final
OL,13,Fcause of death has not yet been
OL,14,Fdetermined.
OL,16,FMr Kohli died at Queen's Medical
OL,17,FCentre in Nottingham on the evening of
OL,18,FSeptember 2, a day after he was
OL,19,Fseriously injured in the park in the
OL,20,FBraunstone Town area of Leicester
OL,21,Fwhile walking his dog Rocky.
