OL,3,CInquest into death of dog walker, 80,
OL,4,Cinvolved in park attack opens
OL,6,FFive children, a boy and a girl aged
OL,7,F14 and one boy and two girls aged 12,
OL,8,Fwere initially arrested on suspicion
OL,9,Fof murder, but four were released
OL,10,Fwithout further action and the 14-year-
OL,11,Fold boy was charged with murder.
OL,13,FThe boy, who cannot be named for legal
OL,14,Freasons, is expected to enter a plea
OL,15,Fto the charge on Friday at Leicester
OL,16,FCrown Court.
OL,18,FTributes paid to Mr Kohli referred to
OL,19,Fhim as a "sweet and gentle soul."
