OL,3,CInquest into death of dog walker, 80,
OL,4,Cinvolved in park attack opens
OL,6,FMr Kohli's family said in a statement
OL,7,Fpreviously released by police: "Bhim
OL,8,Fwas a loving husband, dad and grandad.
OL,9,FHe was also a son, brother and uncle.
OL,11,F"He adored his grandkids with all his
OL,12,Fheart and loved spending time with
OL,13,Fthem. He really was such a loving,
OL,14,Fcaring person whose life was centred
OL,15,Faround his family."
OL,17,FLeicestershire Police said they had
OL,18,Fmade a voluntary referral to the
OL,19,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,20,F(IOPC) because of prior contact with
OL,21,Fthe victim.
