OL,6,FAfter further contact with the
OL,7,Fwatchdog, the force made a mandatory
OL,8,Freferral.
OL,10,FMr Cartwright ended the inquest
OL,11,Fopening by telling Mr Kohli's family:
OL,12,F"I am very sorry for your loss, you
OL,13,Fhave my very sincere condolences."
